flowchart LR
    Code[Write Code] --> Commit[git commit]
    Commit --> Push[git push]
    Push --> CI{CI Pass?}
    CI -->|yes| Review[Code Review]
    CI -->|no| Fix[Fix Errors]
    Fix --> Commit
    Review -->|approved| Merge[Merge to main]
    Review -->|changes requested| Fix
    Merge --> Deploy[Deploy to Staging]
    Deploy --> Test{Tests Pass?}
    Test -->|yes| Release[Release to Production]
    Test -->|no| Rollback[Rollback]
